Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:06.61,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs):\NLike an angel,\Nwho has forsaken sympathy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:06.11,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Planning & Original Story\NGAINAX
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:13.91,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,rise up young boy and\Nmake yourself a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:13.49,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Planning\NPROJECT EVA.\NManga published in\NSHONEN ACE\Nfrom\NKADOKAWA SHOTEN\NPUBLISHING CO., LTD.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:22.29,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,エヴァンゲリオン\NEvangerion (Japanese pronunciation)\NOfficial English: Evangelion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:22.29,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,新世紀\NShin Seiki\NLiteral: New Century
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:29.43,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,Blue skies, and beckoning winds,\Nare trying to open the door of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.79,0:00:25.51,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Character Designs\NYOSHIYUKI SADAMOTO\N\NMecha Design\NIKUTO YAMASHITA\N\NHIDEAKI ANNO
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:29.13,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Assistant Director\NMASAYUKI\NKAZUYA TSURUMAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:37.26,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,But you're gazing at me, as if you cannot see.\NYou just stand there smiling vacantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.59,0:00:32.89,Top Translation,,850,0,0,,Art Director\NHIROSHI KATO\N\NColoring Design\NHARUMI TAKAHOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:35.18,Top Translation,,0,800,0,,Director of Photography\NYOICHI KURODA\N\N\NSound Director\NHIDEYUKI TANAKA\N\NSound Production\NAUDIO TANAKA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:44.27,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,Your eyes, hold such innocence.\NYou're blind to the fate that will soon come to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.07,Top Translation,,600,0,0,,Music\NSHIROH SAGISU\N\NMusic Cooperation\NTV Tokyo Music
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:51.77,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,But it's summoning you, with a touch like a sigh.\NYou seek it without knowing why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:47.82,Bottom Dialog,,0,700,260,,Opening Theme\N"A Cruel Angel's Thesis"\N残酷な天使のテーゼ\NZankoku na Tenshi no Tēze\NLiteral: The Thesis of a Cruel Angel\N\N\N\NLyrics: Neko Oikawa\N\NComposition: Hidetoshi Sato\N\NArrangement: Toshiyuki Ohmori\N\NPerformed by: Yoko Takahashi\N\N\N\N(Star Child Records)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.52,0:00:47.82,Bottom Dialog,,600,0,870,,Closing Theme
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:58.27,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,But someday I know that you will be awakened\N and your eyes will finally see,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.95,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Opening Animation\N\NAnimation\NYUTAKA HONDA\NSHINYA HASEGAWA\N\NEpisode Direction\NKAZUYA TSURUMAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:06.31,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,These wings on your back are just waiting to guide you.\NThe future will soon set you free!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:01.37,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Public Relations\N\NREI ANAMI (TV Tokyo)\NHIROKI SATO (GAINAX)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.50,0:01:03.21,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Animation Production\N\NTATSUNOKO PRO\NGAINAX
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:06.13,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Producer\N\NNORIKO KOBAYASHI\N(TV TOKYO)\N\NYUTAKA SUGIYAMA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:14.35,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,This cruel thesis, a spiteful angel's litany,\Nwill soon soar from the window of your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:14.14,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,TOP SECRET\N\NHuman Instrumentality Project\N\NUnited Nations Executive Council\N17th Interim Report\N\NHuman Instrumentality Committee\NFY2015 Operations Plan Summary\N\NSummary Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:14.35,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,SAMPLE A-01 ADAM\NWho is Adam? He is living. Why?\N\NCaution.....+42.....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.43,0:01:21.85,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,White hot pathos, a desecrated symphony,\NStay true to this and don't betray your mem'ry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:29.57,Bottom Dialog,Yoko Takahashi (GeekyFanDubs),0,0,0,,Come now, reach out. You must embrace reality.\NRise up, young boy, and make yourself a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:23.02,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Director\N\NHideaki Anno
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:29.57,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Production\NTV TOKYO\NNAS
