Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:17.51,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,150,,Female Voice: Unidentified intruder is still coming towards us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:21.52,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: We've got it on visual. I'm putting it on the main screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.00,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: It's been 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:29.01,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Yes. Well now we know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.67,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: The angels are back.
