Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:37.47,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Ah! Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.37,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Every single missile hit the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:49.12,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: No! Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.87,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Ah! Oh. Uh. Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:56.44,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Ahh! Oh. Hh. Hh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.44,0:03:59.91,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Uh. Ahh! Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.98,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Uh. Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:04.88,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Sorry! Get in! Am I real late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.07,0:04:21.85,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Eh. Oh. Ah! Hh. Ohh! Oh. Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:25.55,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: The target's still coming towards us. It's headed straight for Tokyo 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.43,0:04:29.46,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: The air defense force doesn't have enough firepower to stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:32.99,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: Fire everything we've got! Mobilize the Atsugi and Iruma Forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:36.19,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: Don't hold anything back! Destroy that thing at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:52.36,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: It's not possible! That was a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.36,0:04:57.66,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: The tank battalion's been wiped out! Guided missiles and artillery fire seem to have no effect at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:01.16,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: Damn it! We've hit it with everything we've got and we're not even touching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.34,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: Looks like an AT field. Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:06.72,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Yes. Conventional weapons are no match for the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.63,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: I understand, sir. We'll execute backup plan at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.78,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Now wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:22.38,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: No! They're gonna use an N2 mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:23.55,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:24.35,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: (Muffled).
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:38.23,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both: Ooh. Ow! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.85,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both: Oh! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:46.35,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Both: Ohhh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.28,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: Yeah! We did it! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:51.56,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: Well, Ikari, it looks like you won't be getting a shot at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.94,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: Shockwave approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:55.67,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Coughs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:56.72,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:57.01,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:05:59.46,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: But my mouth is full of dirt. Puh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.73,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: You'll be all right. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.70,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Ready to push?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:05.61,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.15,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Push!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:09.39,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Err!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.00,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Giyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:11.77,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.13,0:06:16.55,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Hah! Thanks, Shinji. You're pretty useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.71,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Thank you, but I should thank you, Miss Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.52,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uh, Misato is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:25.64,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: So, Shinji Ikari, we meet at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:26.72,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.95,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: What's the status of the target?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:31.73,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: We're unable to confirm. The EM-pulse knocked everything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:34.27,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: It must be dead. It took the full blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.68,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: External sensors restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:39.29,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: Energy rating at the epicenter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.43,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.23,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: External cameras online.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:44.84,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: What the-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.20,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: That was our last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.45,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: No effect at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:52.85,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: It's a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:03.08,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Yes, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.23,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: His safety is my top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.72,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Look, can you get a car train ready for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.20,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: An express, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:15.97,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Well, I did volunteer to pick him up, so it's only my duty to make sure he gets there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:17.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:24.99,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: (V.O.) Oh, this stinks. I just had this car repaired and it's a total wreck already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:28.71,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: 33 more payments to go, plus the cost of repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:34.11,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: And look, my favorite dress is ruined. Ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.80,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Um, Miss Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.71,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: (V.O.) And I look so good in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.29,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Excuse me, Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:40.15,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Hmm? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:43.69,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Those batteries, isn't that, um, theft?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.37,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uh, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:49.85,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uh, it's an emergency and we needed a working car, right? Heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:54.42,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uh, I am a government official after all, so, everything's gonna be perfectly fine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:55.37,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:58.67,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Mm. I don't think anyone will buy that excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.43,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: You're no fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:03.56,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: You know, you're not as cute as I thought you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.02,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Hmph. Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:06.85,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Ooh, angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:09.19,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.53,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Hahaha. You're just a boy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:14.00,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: You're not as mature as I thought you'd be either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.89,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,(Oorh!) (Aah! Hey watch out! Woah!)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:23.61,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: As we suspected, it's regenerating itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:27.37,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Without that ability, it couldn't operate without support units.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.79,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: Well, quite impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.20,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: It can upgrade its operational parameters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.00,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: And it's also getting smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:41.24,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: It should renew its attack any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:45.84,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: The gates are now closing. Please stand clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:54.24,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: This is a B-22 special express departing from G-33-1. This train will bypass all other stations. Please stand back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.30,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: NERV?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:50.95,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato:Ah-huh! It's a secret organization controlled by the UN.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.20,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: And that's where my father works?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:56.34,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Well, yeah! You do know what he does, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:04.64,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: (Sigh) All my teachers told me, was, that it was important to the future of, mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:12.72,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: Command of this operation is being entrusted to you. Don't betray our trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:13.40,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:17.79,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: Mr. Ikari, we've already seen that our weapons seem to have no effect on these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.10,0:09:20.16,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: That's why we're giving you a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.06,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: Are you sure that you can beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.98,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: That is why NERV exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.94,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Generals: I pray you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:31.12,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: The target is still stationary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:35.64,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Makoto: Estimated current ability to intercept is only 7.5%.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:40.29,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: The UN forces are exhausted. What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.84,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Activate Unit-01.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.52,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: Activate it? But we have no pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:50.59,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Not anymore. Another spare is being delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.35,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Misato, are we going to see my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:56.96,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: (Sigh) Of course. Of course we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:03.45,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Mmm. Father. (Train sounds)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:04.81,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:07.09,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Did your dad send you an ID card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.42,0:10:10.16,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Huh? Umm. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.22,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:13.87,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.13,TS,,0,0,0,,{\fs56.25\1c&H2A2923&\3c&H2A2923&\fnCracked Johnnie\b1\bord0.5\pos(1075.624,790.625)\frz2.036}Come.
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.13,TS,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fnCracked Johnnie\c&H2A2923&\b1\frz17.04\pos(868.429,1076.212)}Ikari\N{\alpha&HFF&}\h      {\alpha}Gendo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.10,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Here, start reading this, okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.81,TS,,0,0,0,,{\fs82.501\fnDFPFuun-W12\b1\frz2.465\c&H0C0C0A&\3c&H041121&\bord1.8\fscx85\fscy88\i1\pos(558.3,667.503)}Welcome to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:20.21,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: NERV.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.13,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: My father's agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.26,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Am I gonna be working for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:25.97,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:29.16,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.69,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: He wouldn't have sent me a letter unless he needed me for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.87,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Hmm. Sounds like you don't get along with your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.30,0:10:38.72,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Huh, you sound just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.96,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Woah! Oh! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.93,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Oh! It's a real GeoFront!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.00,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.27,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: This is our secret underground base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.55,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: NERV Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.08,0:10:56.45,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: This city is the key to rebuilding our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.56,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: A fortress for all mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:01.56,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.27,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,エヴァンゲリオン\NEvangerion (Japanese pronunciation)\NOfficial English: Evangelion
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.27,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,新世紀\NShin Seiki\NLiteral: New Century
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:04.56,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:09.06,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: (Sigh) What on Earth? Isn't this the right way?
