Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.02,0:11:09.06,TS,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fax-0.1\b0\fs37.501\c&H27313F&\fnCambria\i1\pos(299.373,1016.813)}Nerv Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:09.06,TS,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.2\frz23.6\b1\fnLight at the end\c&H59476C&\pos(563.749,1087.189)\blur0.2}Around here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:16.16,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: Central Dogma's closed passages remain sealed. Opening lock B-26 in sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:15.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: It's because of these things that I hate to wear a skirt around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:15.99,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.16,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: I wonder where in the heck Ritsuko is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:21.40,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: I'm sorry. I'm not used to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:24.12,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: We passed this spot twice already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:29.08,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Rrr. Well don't worry about it! They make those transit things to be used you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:41.01,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: Would the chairperson of E Project, Technical Division 1, Dr Ritsuko Akagi, please contact, Captain Misato Katsuragi, of Operations Division 1, immediately.
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.55,TS,,0,0,0,,{\frx340\fry36\frz9.65\move(1280,961.875,1401.251,961.875,24,3110)\c&H030207&\fnArnold 2.1}Air
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.55,TS,,0,0,0,,{\frx340\fry36\frz9.65\move(1280,961.875,1401.251,961.875,24,3110)\bord1.7\3c&H183039&\c&H030207&\blur0.4\fnArnold 2.1}Air
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:42.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: I don't believe it. Is she lost again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.01,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,ここは  です This is
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.75,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uh, hi there, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.16,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.04,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uh, ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:56.11,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Why are you wasting my time, *Captain*?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:58.91,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Don't you know we're short on time *and* manpower?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:11:59.75,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Eheh, Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.72,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: So, is this the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:08.99,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uhh, right. According to the Marduk report, he's the third child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.76,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Hmm. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.40,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Hm? Oh! Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.16,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: I'm afraid he's just like his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.88,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: The gruff and unfriendly part, that is. (Hm)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:19.39,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Handle the rest of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.20,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: Their first meeting in three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.09,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Makoto: Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:28.41,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: Mm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:30.91,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Makoto: It looks like the target's starting to move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.01,0:12:34.31,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: I see. Let's go to battle stations. Level 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:39.12,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: Battle stations. Level 1. Prepare for ground level intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:38.05,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.88,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: It sounds pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:41.51,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: So how's Unit-01 coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:45.01,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: It's currently undergoing refrigeration using the B-type equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.55,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Does it really work? It's never worked before, has it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:55.59,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: The possibility of activation is 0.00000, 00001%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.17,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Around here we just call it the 09 system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:13:00.08,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Does that mean it doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:04.19,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Don't be insulting. It's 09 as in Oni, a Japanese devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:05.00,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:10.23,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Well, anyway! I suppose it's a bit late to be saying, "Sorry it doesn't work."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:16.53,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,左 Left
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.83,0:13:22.63,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Hey! Uh. Eh. Why is it so dark in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.48,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Wuh? Agh! Uh. Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:30.83,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Oh! It's a face! A giant robot! Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:32.87,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: You won't find this in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:33.63,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.25,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: This is man's ultimate fighting machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:39.27,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: The synthetic life form known as Evangelion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:40.17,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Unit-01.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.88,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Built here in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.05,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: It is mankind's last hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.84,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Is this my father's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:49.99,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.99,0:13:50.71,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.36,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:55.59,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:59.71,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Hph. We're moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.76,0:14:04.23,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Moving out? But Unit-00's still in cryostasis! Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.80,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Wait a minute! You're gonna use Unit-01?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.47,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: There's no other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.79,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Now wait! Rei can't do it yet, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:14.85,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: We don't have a pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:17.44,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: We just received one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:19.44,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:21.43,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Shinji Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.46,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.76,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: You will pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:24.31,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:28.04,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: But even Rei Ayanami took seven months to synchronize with her EVA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.68,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: It's impossible for him to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:31.60,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: He *just* *got* here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.44,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: He just has to sit in the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:35.14,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: We don't expect more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:36.04,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Uhh but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:39.05,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Listen, defeating that angel is our ultimate priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:42.21,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: If we have someone who has a chance at synchronizing with an EVA,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:43.60,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: then we've got to risk it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:47.08,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: You do understand that, don't you, *Captain* Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.15,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.21,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Why did, you send for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.26,0:14:58.12,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: You know why I sent for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:03.05,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: So, you're asking me to take this thing, and go out there and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:03.93,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:07.36,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: How could you do this to me? I thought you didn't want me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:10.29,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Why? Why did you have to call me now, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.85,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Because I have a use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:17.07,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: (Video) But why? Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:19.36,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Because there is no one else who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:24.55,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: No, I can't! I've never even seen anything like this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:26.69,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: There's no way I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.24,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: You will be instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:35.91,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: But still! There's no way! I can't pilot that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:42.41,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: If you're going to do it, do it now. If not, then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:54.08,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: It's close. It must sense us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.08,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Shinji, we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.92,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:05.89,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.99,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: This is all wrong. I came all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.20,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Awh, why did I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:16.69,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Why, Shinji? Exactly why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.53,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Uh, eh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:22.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: You mustn't run away. You must confront your father, and you must confront yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:26.51,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Rrr, I know that! But I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.04,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Fuyutsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:36.80,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: (Video) Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:38.48,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Wake up Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.33,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: Can we use her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.88,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: She's not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:44.13,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:46.80,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.03,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rei: (Whispers) Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:51.17,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Our spare is unusable. You will do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:51.92,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rei: Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:57.47,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Reconfigure Unit-01 system for Rei, then activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.88,0:17:00.80,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: Roger. Calling off current program, and beginning activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:06.25,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: I knew it! Huh. I'm not needed after all. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.39,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:28.81,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rei: Ahh. Hf. Ohh. Hu. Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:38.60,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rei: Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.01,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Woah. Owh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.15,0:17:41.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:43.19,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:44.49,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:47.15,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.52,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Makoto: The EVA activated itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:55.83,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Makoto: It ripped right out of the right arm restraint!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:58.04,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: No! That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.17,0:18:00.29,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: The entry plug wasn't even inserted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:01.80,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: That just can't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:05.20,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Hah, you mean it reacted without any kind of interface?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:09.08,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Was it really to protect something? To protect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.41,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Hah. It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.96,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rei: Heh. Ah! Hf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:21.12,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Uh. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:28.39,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Rei: Eeh! Aah! Ehuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:31.89,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shiji: Huh? Ohh. Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:37.85,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away. I mustn't *run away*!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:42.15,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: I'll do it! I'll pilot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.96,0:18:46.96,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: (Radio) Cooling process completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:48.81,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,Left
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.68,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Right arm repairs completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:50.65,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Cage now in position for docking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:54.37,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: Signal plug terminator now being ejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.48,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: (Radio) Roger. Insert an entry plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.72,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Plug locked in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.11,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Connecting UNIT-01.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:10.65,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.59,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.07,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Uh, what is this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:20.52,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Ooh. Wao-! (Muffled) Mm! Mm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.62,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:24.17,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Once your lungs are filled with LCL,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.65,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: your blood will be oxygenated directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.96,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: (Radio) It's okay. You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.62,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: (Garbled) I'm gonna be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:35.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Stop complaining. You're a boy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:40.16,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,高圧電流 High Voltage
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.64,0:19:38.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: (Radio) Connecting main power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:40.24,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: All circuits transmitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Female Voice: (Radio) Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.03,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: (Radio) Connecting secondary contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.36,0:19:44.87,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:47.32,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: A-10 NERV connection normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.17,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Configure the language logic interface for Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:55.71,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: All preliminary contacts established. Performance nominal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:55.05,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:57.37,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: Bi-directional circuits are open.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.56,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: Synchronization ratio at 41.3%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.25,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:04.45,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: Harmonics seem to be normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:06.04,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: I see no disturbances.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.68,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:10.61,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Mmm! Begin launch sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.76,0:20:12.59,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Beginning launch sequence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:16.68,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Removing primary lock bolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:18.12,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Removal confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.61,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Removing the umbilical bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.47,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Removing secondary lock bolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:28.58,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,安全 + 第一 Safety First
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.98,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Removing primary restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.52,0:20:32.46,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Removing secondary restraints.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:38.01,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Releasing safety locks number 1 through 15!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:41.35,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: Internal batteries fully charged!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:44.57,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Male Voice: External battery outlet closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:47.60,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: Roger. Move EVA Unit-01 to the launch pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.48,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,危険 Danger     保ゴ めがね Wear safety glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.25,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibuki: Launch path clear. All systems green.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.93,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko: Evangelion, ready for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.99,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Understood! Can we really do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.00,0:21:16.33,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Of course. Unless we defeat the Angels, we have no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:19.71,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki: Ikari, are you absolutely certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:21.42,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Gendo: Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.52,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: EVA launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:23.09,Top Translation,,0,0,0,,危険 Danger\N保ゴ めがね\NWear safety glasses
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:24.57,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:52.92,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinji: Woah! Huh. Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.80,Bottom Dialog,,0,0,0,,Misato: Shinji, don't get killed out there.
